Comment: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:38.81,Title,,0,0,0,,Free from the Spell! \NThe Great Warrior Sheds Tears!!
Comment: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:36.02,Title,,0,0,0,,Eternal Friends! \NThe Vowed Bell Echoes Across the Mighty Seas!!
